### Get all ground truth definitions (no filter)
GET http://localhost:5105/api/groundtruth/definitions
Accept: application/json

### Get ground truth definitions with filter: status=Validated
GET http://localhost:5105/api/groundtruth/definitions?ValidationStatus=Validated
Accept: application/json

### Get ground truth definitions with filter: tag=defect, createdBy=user1@company.com
GET http://localhost:5105/api/groundtruth/definitions?Tag=defect&CreatedBy=user1@company.com
Accept: application/json

### Get ground truth definitions with multiple filters (example: status=Validated, tag=quality, createdAfter=2024-01-01)
GET http://localhost:5105/api/groundtruth/definitions?ValidationStatus=Validated&Tag=quality&CreatedAfter=2024-01-01
Accept: application/json

### Get a specific ground truth definition by ID (replace {id} with actual GUID)
GET http://localhost:5105/api/groundtruth/definitions/{id}
Accept: application/json
